<div id='gazette_story'>
    <div align='center'>
        <font size='4'><b>Trix, Toys, and Games</b></font><br>
                                <img src='http://graphics.millsberry.com/site_gfx/interiors/gazette/gazette_20100603.jpg' border='1' width='280' height='200'>
                        </div>
        <div id='gazette_byline'><em>By Audrey Smythe-Wei<br>Editor-in-Chief</em></div>
        <b>Thursday, June  3, 2010</b> &mdash;
    Downtown just got a little more <i>swirled</i> up! And if you don&#039;t know what we mean, then it&#039;s time you check out  <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">Trix, Toys, and Games</a>. No, we didn&#039;t misspell &quot;tricks&quot;...we meant &quot;<i>Trix</i>&reg;!: that delicious, fruity, <i>swirly</i> cereal that unlocks your imagination and takes you to a fantastical world&mdash;exclusively for kids!&quot;<br><br>We got wind of the news just the other day, when one curious resident wondered, &quot;Is the store still the same as before, back when it was called <i>Tricks</i>, Toys, and Games?&quot;<br><br>Sources, we&#039;re happy to report, tell us <i>yes of course</i>! You can still get every sort of fun at the novelties shop&mdash;from your favorite <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">skateboard</a> to a silly <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">pet rock</a>&mdash;but you&#039;ll <i>also</i> be able to find new Trix-cereal-inspired items that will transport you to places beyond your coolest Trix-filled dreams!<br>
<br>
To start, buy yourself a mural of a <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7"><i>pegasus in the sky</i></a> and hang it on your wall. Or purchase a <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7"><i>Berry-Berry Blue Island mural </i></a> to go with your new <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7"><i>berry-blue sword</i></a> made of Trix!<br><br>One happy-go-lucky shopper commented, &quot;Personally, I love the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">banana boat</a>...especially when it&#039;s placed right next to my <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">silly rabbit shadow</a>!&quot; <br><br>There&#039;s a ton of great stuff for sale&mdash;but take special care to hold on to your <i>boxes of Trix cereal</i> as you head home! Why&#039;s that? Well, even though Trix is just for kids, that silly rabbit can&#039;t help but try to get his white paws on the deliciously fruity, swirly cereal.<br><br>So head to the new <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">Trix, Toys, and Games</a>; pick up something fruity and fun; hold on tight to your Trix; and let your imagination run wild!
    </div>

